<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Así es como se llamará la pestaña en el navegador</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Este es un gran encabezado.</h1>
    <p>Esto es sólo un párrafo de texto</p>
    <h2>Y ésta es una cabecera un poco más pequeña</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>Este es un elemento de una lista de viñetas (la primera)</li>
        <li>Y este es el segundo elemento</li>
    </ul>

    <img src="https://e1.pxfuel.com/desktop-wallpaper/266/862/desktop-wallpaper-car-for-pc-3d.jpg" alt="Image 1">

    <!-- YouTube -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-youtube">
        <div class="iframe-label">▶ YouTube</div>
        <iframe width="560" height="315"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xkOqo3yggHk?si=uNwl4XSm-a8MiS0U"
            title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Google Maps -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-maps">
        <div class="iframe-label">📍 Mapa</div>
        <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3976.8!2d-74.0721!3d4.7109!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zBMKwNDInMzkuMiJOIDc0wrAwNCcxOS42Ilc!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sco!4v1620000000000"
            width="100%" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Windy -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-windy">
        <div class="iframe-label">🌬️ Viento</div>
        <iframe
            src="https://embed.windy.com/embed2.html?lat=4.711&lon=-74.072&zoom=5&level=surface&overlay=wind&menu=&message=true&marker=&forecast=12&calendar=&pressure=&type=map&location=coordinates&detail=&detailLat=4.711&detailLon=-74.072&metricWind=km%2Fh&metricTemp=%C2%B0C"
            width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0"></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Spotify -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-spotify">
        <div class="iframe-label">🎵 Spotify</div>
        <iframe
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/37i9dQZF1DXcBWIGoYBM5M"
            width="100%" height="380" frameborder="0"
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
            loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Reloj -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-reloj">
        <div class="iframe-label">🕐 Reloj</div>
        <iframe
            src="https://free.timeanddate.com/clock/i8qth6ty/n1370/fn6/fs24/fc000/tct/pct/brt/ahl/tt0/ta1"
            width="100%" height="200" frameborder="0"></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- Ventusky -->
    <div class="iframe-wrapper iframe-ventusky">
        <div class="iframe-label">🌡️ Temperatura</div>
        <iframe
            src="https://embed.ventusky.com/?p=4.7;-74.1;6&l=temperature"
            width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
